297
00:15:43,160 --> 00:15:44,160
You know exactly

298
00:15:44,680 --> 00:15:45,960
what I'm capable of.

299
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,960
If it wasn't you,

300
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:54,960
