308
00:16:13,160 --> 00:16:13,720
Gang,

309
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:16,520
are you really planning
to hide him forever?

310
00:16:18,640 --> 00:16:21,280
That old guy's a ticking time bomb.

311
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:23,200
