314
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:33,080
Gang,

315
00:16:34,240 --> 00:16:34,840
maybe we should

316
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:38,200
take care of him while he's

317
00:16:38,444 --> 00:16:39,466
in our control...

318
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:54,720
Slowly.

319
00:17:06,560 --> 00:17:07,200
