375
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:49,640
I'll head out now.

376
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:51,360
Go ahead.

377
00:18:52,470 --> 00:18:53,360
Thanks.

378
00:18:53,360 --> 00:18:54,620
Don't mention it. I'll leave now.

379
00:18:54,622 --> 00:18:55,222
Thank you.

