432
00:21:29,750 --> 00:21:30,911
That's very thoughtful of you.

433
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:34,920
Mr. Qi. Mr. Sun.

434
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:35,822
We brought him home.

435
00:21:35,866 --> 00:21:36,350
Xiaoguang.

436
00:21:36,355 --> 00:21:36,977
Yuan!

437
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:37,720
